<Layout title="About CrazyQuizzes" description="Learn about CrazyQuizzes — the home of free personality quizzes, trivia blitz games, and emoji challenges online.">
  <div class="page-badge">★ WHO ARE WE</div>
  <h1 class="page-title">ABOUT<br><span style="color:#6c3bff;">CRAZYQUIZZES</span></h1>
  <div class="page-body">
    <p>CrazyQuizzes is the internet's premier destination for quizzes that tell you what kind of pizza topping matches your personality, how deep your Y2K nostalgia really goes, and exactly which toxic trait you're projecting onto the group chat.</p>
    <p>We make no claims of scientific accuracy. Our algorithm has zero credentials. Every result you get is 100% made up by people who had too much fun doing it.</p>

    <h2>WHAT WE DO</h2>
    <p>We build personality quizzes, blitz trivia rounds, and chaos-inducing micro-tests that are designed to be shared, debated, and screenshot at 2am. If you're still thinking about your result tomorrow, we've done our job.</p>

    <h2>THE TEAM</h2>
    <p>CrazyQuizzes is a small, independent project run by people who believe the internet should be a little more fun and a lot less serious. We're not a corporation. There are no focus groups. Every quiz gets made because someone thought it would be funny.</p>

    <h2>THE VIBE</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Chaotic-good energy at all times</li>
      <li>Y2K aesthetic, 2026 sensibility</li>
      <li>No right answers (except on the trivia ones)</li>
      <li>Results shared liberally to group chats worldwide</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>CONTACT US</h2>
    <p>Got a quiz idea, a complaint, or a genuinely unhinged suggestion? <a href="/contact">Hit us up.</a> We read everything, respond to some of it, and screenshot the best ones.</p>
  </div>
